  8592 | 
  8593 |   // Test if the FCmpInst instruction is used exclusively by a select as
  8594 |   // part of a minimum or maximum operation. If so, refrain from doing
  8595 |   // any other folding. This helps out other analyses which understand
  8596 |   // non-obfuscated minimum and maximum idioms, such as ScalarEvolution
